==Finnish==
{{Finnish index|vo}}

===Interjection===
'''voi'''

#[[oh]]
#:''voi ei!'' (oh no!)

===Noun===
'''voi'''
====Etymology====
From the same Finno-Ugric root *''woye'' as Hungarian [[vaj]]

#[[butter]]

====Derived terms====
*[[voidella]]
*[[voinen]]
*[[voisilmä]]
*[[voiveitsi]]

===Verb===
'''voi''' (third person sg. present indicative, and part of sg. present negative of ''[[voida]]'')

# [[can]]

===Usage===
*''hän voi auttaa'' (she can help)
*''minä en voi auttaa'' (I cannot help)
*''hän ei voi auttaa'' (she cannot help)

